The paper proposes a new approach for structured data representation using discriminative information and latent variable models. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
